					"type": 23,
					"value": "CTY_Main_A\r\nTODO: oe command\r\n* Goto Sharess Caress in Wyrms' Crossing (BGO_Main_A), talk to the Bartender. Agree to drink Potent Drink.\r\n* Go back to the Lower City.\r\n* Drink Potent brew and drink any other alchohol at the same time.\r\n* Repeat a few times."
